ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: A good introductory course. It is an undergraduate course, so it can only provide a graduate student with a basic overview. However, the final paper requirement might be useful to start your own research.
Highly recommend taking as an introductory course

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: It was a comprehensive overview of the subject. It was however too basic to equip me with new tools. The final paper requirement helped me as a commitment device to start my research for my M.Sc. dissertation.
Good prerequisite to additional economics coursework
